org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core
Class CloudSimTags

java.lang.Object
  org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core.CloudSimTags

public final class CloudSimTags
extends java.lang.Object

Contains various static command tags that indicate a type of action that needs to be undertaken by CloudSim entities when they receive or send events.
NOTE: To avoid conflicts with other tags, CloudSim reserves negative numbers, 0 - 299, and 9600.

Since:
CloudSim Toolkit 1.0
Author:
Manzur Murshed, Rajkumar Buyya, Anthony Sulistio

public static final int ABRUPT_END_OF_SIMULATION
Denotes an abrupt end of simulation. That is, one event of this type is enough for CloudSimShutdown to trigger the end of the simulation
